 Gel Pen.\n## Features To Look For\nWhen choosing a gel pen, there are several features to consider. These include:\n1. **Ink Type**: As discussed earlier, water-based vs. alcohol-based gel pens.\n2. **Color Selection**: Consider whether you prefer a wide range of colors or a limited selection.\n3. **Bonding Capacity**: If you plan to write on dark-colored paper or fabrics, look for a gel pen with good bonding capacity.\n4. **Smoothness**: Check if the gel pen glides smoothly across the page.\n5. **Dry Time**: Look for a gel pen that dries quickly to avoid smearing.\n6. **Durability**: Opt for a high-quality gel pen that lasts longer and doesn't dry out easily.\nBy considering these factors, you can narrow down your options and find the best gel pen for your needs.\nConclusion\nChoosing the best gel pen depends on your personal preferences and requirements. Whether you're looking for a smooth writing experience, vibrant colors, or quick drying time, there's a gel pen out there for everyone. By following our tips on how to choose the best gel pens, you can find the perfect pen for all your writing and drawing needs. Happy shopping!", "cool_products": [{"title": "Helix Oxford Colour Gel Pens (x10 Pack Assorted Colours) with Plastic Free Packaging, 10 Count (Pack of 1)", "clickurl": "http://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B07KCQM1XZ?tag=wvf6tvg6e849vru4-20", "brand": "Helix", "image_s": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/515tfBUm2JS._SL75_.jpg", "image_m": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/515tfBUm2JS._SL160_.jpg", "image_l": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/515tfBUm2JS._SL500_.jpg"}, {"title": "Mutsitaz 48 Packs Color Gel Ink Pens Set for Adult Colouring Books,Drawing,and Writing Manga Markers with 1.0mm Tip (12 Metallic,12 Glitter,12 Neon,12 Water Chalk)", "clickurl": "http://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B07VCJDQK6?tag=wvf6tvg6e849vru4-20", "brand": "Mutsitaz", "image_s": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51BziuHLawL._SL75_.jpg", "image_m": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/